This paper proposes a model for Audio Visual Scene-aware Dialog (AVSD) task, which involves multiple modalities including video and dialogue history. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely categories as the paper focuses on generating dialogue based on video context.
